      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is priced to reflect its history as a hardworking daily driver. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear but remains functional with no major odors. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it would benefit from a routine tune-up and new tires soon. It\u2019s an honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation.",
