      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in peerless condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the immaculate exterior, reflects a standard of care synonymous with showroom delivery. Mechanically irreproachable and aesthetically flawless, this remains an exceptional opportunity for the collector or enthusiast seeking an uncompromising driving experience.",
